firesting2 <- firesting |>
  select(c(1:3,5:9)) |> 
  rename(TIME = `Time (HH:MM:SS)`, 
         dTIME = `Time (s)`,

         ch3 = Ch3...7, 
         ch4 = Ch4...8,

  select(c("dTIME",all_of(chamber),"TIME","temperature"))
